title: [RECRUITING] Tryouts for RKLe5 Gaming Begin Soon!

embed.description: For business inquiries: rkle5gamingofficial@gmail.com Hello, we are RKLe5 Gaming. Mercy will not be shown. Sympathy will not be given. We are RKLe5. ~ RKLe5 ...

body:
RKLe5 Gaming is holding tryouts in 1 hour and 45 minutes (that's 2:30 AWST), if you're interested in joining please remember the following:
* The team you're placed in will be based on skill and not rank. (Though rank will be used to even out the teams).
* Toxicity is a big NO, this will get you no where in anything.
* All ranks and levels are welcome to come and try out!
* You need to be able to be active on LoL if you get into the team, we ask for your full commitment.

Join by adding "Mr Zeroxs" and messaging me to say you'll be playing.
Thank you for reading, good luck to all and we'll see you on the rift! {{champion:17}} 
~ RKLe5 Zeroxs, Owner of RKLe5 Gaming.
